txt.en: 'We did it! Fighting by your side truly is exhilarating. I feel like the four of us could even take on Dushtalbúk himself!'
'The advisors are dead, then? I knew you could manage it, [placeholder]. I never doubted you for a moment, let alone two or three!'
Warlord Dushtalbúk's advisors should be defeated if you can find them within Shakhajât.
Molkha waits for your report about the warlord's advisors.
'While we're in Shakhajât, we should keep an eye out for those hobgoblin advisors we saw with Dushtalbúk. They will be much easier to deal with if we catch them on their own!'
'If you want to head back into Shakhajât, we should keep an eye out for those hobgoblin advisors we saw with Dushtalbúk. They will be much easier to deal with if we catch them on their own!'
Molkha thinks you should keep an eye out for the advisors to Warlord Dushtalbúk while you storm Shakhajât.
